creator: Fun Quarter
descriptionHtml:
Treasure Planet: Drill&Mine is a relaxing simulation game.
Drive your truck in different treasure planets, use your drills to crush gem mines, collect and sell colorful gems, upgrade your trucks, and become rich.

Game Features:
A large number of treasure planets
Dig for a variety of rare and precious gems
Upgrade your trucks and drills
Dress up your trucks with a variety of decorations
Use drills to unlock your wealth code
descriptionShort: Welcome to Treasure Planet, where the drill is your code to wealth!
title: Treasure Planet : Drill&Mine
